Interface DrugQuota

All Known Implementing Classes:
DrugQuotaRow
public interface DrugQuota

Represents a single row of the Drug_Quota table.

Some relevant facts about this interface:

  • It represents the data that can be stored and retrieved from the Drug_Quota table in the database.
  • It has 5 columns, all of which have getter and setter methods.
